- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as consistent query answering is a problem in AI and the paper discusses algorithmic and complexity theoretic results.
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses different classes of repairs and their computational properties.
